ğŸ“Œ Project Overview
This project focuses on analyzing drug-related data to uncover key insights such as:
Most commonly prescribed drugs.
Drug classes categorized as Rx (prescription) vs. OTC (over-the-counter).
Common side effects and their frequency.
Pregnancy safety categories and alcohol interactions.
CSA (Controlled Substances Act) classification of drugs.
